{"word":"G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o - Anoint","slug":"G5548","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chríō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khree'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Anoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - chrio&#x0304;</b> - <i>khree'-o</i><p/>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5530\">G5530</a> through the idea of <i>contact</i>; to <i>smear</i> or <i>rub</i> with oil, that is, (by implication) to <i>consecrate</i> to an office or religious service: - anoint."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G500\">G500</a>, <a href=\"#/G5545\">G5545</a>, <a href=\"#/G5546\">G5546</a>, <a href=\"#/G5547\">G5547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580\">G5580</a>"}]}